<item>
            <title>[LU-17575] Require specific enable flag for lfs migrate -m (directory migration)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17575</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We know that there are still major corruption possibilities with lfs migrate -m (directory migration).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Let&apos;s add a warning and require a flag to enable this functionality&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="81021">LU-17575</key>
            <summary>Require specific enable flag for lfs migrate -m (directory migration)</summary>
